                  <join result="persNamePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17200115-46-defend236 t17200115-46-defloc232"></join>, was indicted for the <rs id="t17200115-46-off233" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17200115-46-off233" type="offenceCategory" value="kill"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17200115-46-off233" type="offenceSubcategory" value="murder"></interp>
               Murder of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17200115-46-victim238" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Davis 
                        <interp inst="t17200115-46-victim238" type="surname" value="Davis"></interp>
